@drew-dectech Are you okay with this approach or would you like to finish this PR?

@vidakovic, it is an upgrade. This is related to the https://activemq.apache.org/security-advisories.data/CVE-2023-46604-announcement.txt security issue:

> Users are recommended to upgrade to version 5.15.16, 5.16.7, 5.17.6, or 5.18.3, which fixes this issue.


Originally, our docker container was based on `5.15.9` and this is tries to upgrade it to `5.18.3`

@oyinig Please follow the required PR and commit message pattern:
FINERACT-XXXX: Short description

FINERACT-XXXX: is the story id which this PR is relates to.

@josehernandezfintecheandomx Please check my comments and please modify the PR title and the commit message:

Fineract modularisation tracked in this story: https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FINERACT-1932 

Please use this in the PR and in the commit message!
